{"tid":2371565,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"半島電視台揭露疫情初期 中國如何審查資訊流通","createTime":"2021-01-19T03:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T03:43:08.000Z","uid":134993,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7b8028109ab2966ddccffad72afb2f6788a4a8","tid":2371565,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:39:23.000Z","msg":"「外界普遍認為，中國政府在最開始那幾天不說明和不透明，是病毒得以如此迅速散播的原因之一，造就了超過200萬人病故的這場百年大疫。」<br />\n<br />\n「在武漢，人員和設備雙缺，導致許多感染病患求醫治無門。可笑的是，醫院隱瞞了真相。」<br />\n<br />\nNew videos show Wuhan during earliest days of COVID outbreak<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/1/18/new-footage-shows-wuhan-during-earliest-days-of-covid-pandemic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2F1%2F18%2Fnew-footage-shows-wuhan-during-earliest-days-of-covid-pandemic&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrBn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=d8af6d57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/1/18/new-footage-shows-wuhan-during-earliest-days-of-covid-pandemic</a><br />\n<br />\n公布武漢封城前關鍵3天畫面 半島電視台：中國隱匿疫情<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202101180302.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202101180302.aspx&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrBn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=0fd121cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202101180302.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"f736955c2c9191ec31ec5b8a104bb9c6d420596d","tid":2371565,"uid":134993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:42:20.000Z","msg":"兩名記者拍攝的畫面和撰寫的日記同時也揭露了當局如何地試圖阻撓記者工作，即使兩人任職於北京的國營媒體，並已取得武漢巿政府媒體主管機關許可。<br />\n<br />\n從武漢華南海鮮批發市場，到不同醫院，公安在每一個轉角都試圖阻礙記者報導。"},{"pid":"c03058b4ca7f0d978079957b241d67925cd49dcd","tid":2371565,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"陳偉在日記中寫道，相對而言，武漢已經恢復正常，「人們不想再談疫情，彷彿那段歷史早已遠去。人們覺得活在中國非常幸運、驕傲，因為那是唯一控制病毒的國家。」<br />\n<br />\n他寫道：「這也許不是事實，但大部分中國人卻是這麼認為。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51be62b7502e9fb8323c450edbfb3ec5e348977e","tid":2371565,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}